  "prompt": "Do any of the Indian banks provide personalized gift cards where I can put a personalized image on the card?",
  "response": "Yes, some Indian banks do provide personalized gift cards where you can add a personalized image. As of now, one of the prominent banks offering this service is HDFC Bank. They have a feature known as \"MyDesign Card\" where customers can customize their gift cards with a personal image or design.\n\nTo avail this service, you might need to visit the bank's official website or a branch for specific instructions on how to personalize your gift card. Always check for the latest updates directly from the bank, as services and offerings can change.",
